description: Yaqeen Saudi Equity ETF aims to provide investors with long term capital appreciation and growth. The Fund passively invests in the listed Saudi equities in order to achieve the results that correspond to the performance, before fees and expenses, of the Benchmark Index. The Fund is passively managed by way of fully investing, barring a small cash portion, into the components of the Benchmark Index in the same weightings with the aim of replicating the performance of the Index.
name: YAQEEN Saudi Equity ETF
